title: (Tues Early Bird) Someone Stole From Bobby’s House + Songs That Put Us In A Good Mood!
itunes:title: (Tues Early Bird) Someone Stole From Bobby’s House + Songs That Put Us In A Good Mood!
description:
Bobby shares the theft he witnessed with his own eyes from his house that he couldn’t believe. And why Amy believes she saw her dad on the 1-year anniversary of his passing. We each share new songs that instantly put us in a good mood!
